metadata.name: PHOENIX
metadata.description:
My body is my journal, and my tattoos are my story.
I create my journey , rise from ashes and succeed in my own story, my way.

I am THE WOMAN.

One of the most beautiful creation of God is Woman. Women possess immense power to conquer the world and write their own journey intertwined by multiple stories.
A women’s story is of happiness, hardship, heartbreak, love & affection. 

A women’s body transforms throughout her life starting from being an adult, to getting married , to becoming a mother and a grand mother and her body emotes the story of her life. The women’s body is like a canvas which has many stories to be told, not to be told and every story is unique filled with joy, laughter, happiness, sadness, sorrow which defines the journey of her life.

A woman rises, falls and again rises just like a phoenix to emerge like a winner and make the world a better place for us to live.

We are the Women.

Location - India
Edition - 1/1
Dimension - 3078 X 4617

Year - 2022
